## 💍 Frequently Asked Questions from Fort Lauderdale Brides

**"When should I book my bridal makeup artist?"**
For peak South Florida wedding season — October through April — we recommend booking **8 to 12 months in advance**. Our calendar fills quickly, and we only take a limited number of weddings per week to ensure every bride receives our full attention.

**"Do you travel to my venue?"**
Absolutely. We serve brides throughout **Fort Lauderdale, Miami, Boca Raton, Palm Beach, the Florida Keys**, and beyond. Travel fees may apply for locations outside of Broward County.

**"Can you accommodate a large bridal party?"**
Yes! We coordinate beautifully for full bridal parties. Our team ensures everyone — bridesmaids, mothers of the bride and groom, flower girls — feels beautiful and cared for.

**"What if I have sensitive skin or specific skin concerns?"**
We love a challenge. During your consultation, we discuss every concern — rosacea, hyperpigmentation, dryness, oiliness — and choose products specifically suited to your skin. Your comfort is always our priority.

